{"type":null,"faqId":26071,"title":"拍照时能否记录位置信息？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>使用平板拍照时，可以将拍照地点的位置信息添加到所拍摄的照片中。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90973\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>为方便记录位置信息，请在平板连网状态下使用此功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.1.1\"></a><span>在主屏幕界面，点击“设置 &gt; 定位服务”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.2.1\"></a><span>点击或滑动“访问我的位置信息”后的开关至 “</span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.2.1.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.2.1.2.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90974\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开启定位功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<a name=\"figd0e430\"><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.2.1.3.1\"></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90975\" style=\"width:2.6680555in;height:3.932639in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.3.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.3.1\"></a><span>在主屏幕界面，点击“相机 &gt; </span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.3.1.1.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.3.1.1.2.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90976\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.18472221in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 设置”，点击或滑动“地理位置”后的开关至 “</span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.3.1.3.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.3.1.3.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90977\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.2.4.1\"></a><span>点击拍照即可记录拍摄地点的位置信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>使用平板拍摄照片后，您可以在照片浏览界面点击 “</span><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.3.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.3.2.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90978\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.18472221in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“菜单 &gt; 详细信息”中查看该照片的位置信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.4\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90979\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":167,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"391","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Camera-Picture","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1432262698000,"seriesProductName":"T1-A21w","visitedTimes":17,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"拍照,照相,位置,地点,坐标,定位","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}